      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force compared to N=11 experimental constructs. Mean predicted yield force 1423 N versus mean experimental 1451 N (1.9% difference). E/uval = 0.61, well within acceptance bounds. Both laboratories show consistent results with no statistically significant inter-laboratory bias detected.",
      "quantityOfInterest": "Yield force (N)",
